p #[strong Project Nevada:] Outdated, inefficient, bloated, and broken. Most features have modern alternatives (See the list below). Has almost 20 scripts that run every single frame, causes save bloat due to continuous quest stages being triggered, and some features either don't work or break the game (Chargeable weapons, lethal headshots, and the stealth/AI changes).
